1
00:00:00,601 --> 00:00:03,222
“Beauty over power.”

2
00:00:03,222 --> 00:00:05,329
Where does that come from?

3
00:00:05,329 --> 00:00:07,210
It comes from Guru Mahārāj.

4
00:00:09,713 --> 00:00:11,158
And if you read
in the beginning of

5
00:00:11,158 --> 00:00:12,678
The Search for Sri Krṣṇa.

6
00:00:12,678 --> 00:00:14,862
Very beautiful.

7
00:00:14,862 --> 00:00:16,008
I mean …

8
00:00:16,023 --> 00:00:18,160
I got to place it there.

9
00:00:18,160 --> 00:00:21,063
Why did it appear there?

10
00:00:21,063 --> 00:00:23,385
Did I put it there?

11
00:00:23,385 --> 00:00:27,641
Or was I used by
some higher power

12
00:00:27,641 --> 00:00:31,319
to place it there?

13
00:00:31,319 --> 00:00:36,106
I would subscribe to the latter.

14
00:00:36,106 --> 00:00:38,736
I do not know anything about
Kṛṣṇa consciousness.

15
00:00:42,539 --> 00:00:44,068
But Guru Mahārāj [does],

16
00:00:44,068 --> 00:00:46,216
[and] offering ourselves
in service to him

17
00:00:46,216 --> 00:00:47,361
and his conception,

18
00:00:47,361 --> 00:00:48,444
something appeared there.

19
00:00:48,444 --> 00:00:50,467
So, if you look in the very beginning,

20
00:00:50,467 --> 00:00:51,889
what does it say?

21
00:00:51,889 --> 00:00:58,007
Beauty is the ultimate
controlling principle.

22
00:00:58,007 --> 00:01:02,956
It’s greater than power.

23
00:01:02,956 --> 00:01:06,033
So thematically, Guru Mahārāj,

24
00:01:06,033 --> 00:01:09,498
he has certain themes,
seed concept themes,

25
00:01:09,506 --> 00:01:11,749
that he revisits continuously. 

26
00:01:11,749 --> 00:01:15,438
One is: form versus substance,

27
00:01:15,444 --> 00:01:19,040
or substance over form.

28
00:01:19,040 --> 00:01:21,558
Beauty over power.

29
00:01:21,558 --> 00:01:23,789
Mercy over justice.

30
00:01:23,789 --> 00:01:27,659
Heart over intellect.

31
00:01:27,659 --> 00:01:30,750
He has a consistent system.

32
00:01:30,750 --> 00:01:32,837
So, talking about

33
00:01:32,838 --> 00:01:34,665
Beauty over power, means:

34
00:01:34,665 --> 00:01:37,273
which is a greater force?

35
00:01:37,273 --> 00:01:41,420
Beauty or what we generally
conceive of as power?

36
00:01:41,420 --> 00:01:44,005
There are so many examples in history

37
00:01:44,005 --> 00:01:47,992
of the most powerful man, 

38
00:01:47,992 --> 00:01:53,026
coming under the sway of
a beautiful girl.

39
00:01:53,076 --> 00:01:56,293
There are historic examples of this 
all over the world.

40
00:01:56,293 --> 00:01:58,315
North, South, East and West.

41
00:01:58,315 --> 00:02:00,661
The most powerful man

42
00:02:00,661 --> 00:02:03,248
comes under the control

43
00:02:03,248 --> 00:02:06,456
of the beauty of a young girl.

44
00:02:06,463 --> 00:02:11,040
That’s an example of 
beauty over power.

